## CLI Quick Reference

### Session Commands

```bash
# Check session status
agentic status
```

### Logging Commands

```bash
# Record a decision
agentic decision --title "Decision Title" --rationale "Why this decision was made"

# Record an assumption
agentic assumption --assumption "Assumption Title" --rationale "Basis for assumption"
```

### Handoff Commands

{% if next_agent_id %}
```bash
# Handoff to next agent (artifacts relative to artifacts/ directory)
agentic handoff --to {{ next_agent_id }} --artifacts "{{ agent_id}}_{{ agent_slug }}/{{ produces.core[0].filename if produces.core else 'artifact_name.md' }}" --notes "Handoff notes"
```
{% else %}
```bash
# End workflow (terminal agent)
agentic end
```
{% endif %}

